'''釙化鋰'''是一種[[無機化合物|無機化合物]]，化學式為Li<sub>2</sub>Po。它是一种[[钋化物|钋化物]]，一系列化学稳定的钋化合物。<ref name="G&E">{{Greenwood&Earnshaw1st|page=899}}</ref><ref name=Moyer>{{citation | last = Moyer | first = Harvey V. | contribution = Chemical Properties of Polonium | pages = 33–96 | title = Polonium | url = http://www.osti.gov/bridge/servlets/purl/4367751-nEJIbm/ | editor-last = Moyer | editor-first = Harvey V. | id = TID-5221 | doi = 10.2172/4367751 | year = 1956 | location = Oak Ridge, Tenn. | publisher = United States Atomic Energy Commission}}.</ref>

== 制備 ==
可將[[釙化氫|釙化氫]]與[[鋰|鋰]]反應而制得。<ref name="G&E"/><ref name=Moyer/>
:H<sub>2</sub>Po + 2Li → Li<sub>2</sub>Po + H<sub>2</sub>

它也可以由钋和锂在 300–400 °C直接反应而成。<ref name=Bagnall/>

== 晶體結構 ==
晶體結構同於[[釙化鈉|釙化鈉]]，為反[[螢石|螢石]]型結構<ref name="G&E">{{Greenwood&Earnshaw1st|page=899}}</ref><ref name="AEC-chem">{{citation | last = Moyer | first = Harvey V. | contribution = Chemical Properties of Polonium | pages = 33–96 | title = Polonium | url = http://www.osti.gov/bridge/servlets/purl/4367751-nEJIbm/ | editor-last = Moyer | editor-first = Harvey V. | id = TID-5221 | doi = 10.2172/4367751 | year = 1956 | location = Oak Ridge, Tenn. | publisher = United States Atomic Energy Commission | accessdate = 2011-08-11 | archive-date = 2019-07-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190701105103/https://www.osti.gov/biblio/4367751 | dead-url = no }}.</ref>

